graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>React + Node.js]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime environment| NodeJS[Node.js 22+]
    Dashboard -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    Dashboard -->|OAuth + Routes| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    Dashboard -->|auth proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React 18]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6]
    Dashboard -->|backend framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient["@kubernetes/client-node"]

    %% Internal ODH Component Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|watches CRDs| OdhOperator[ODH/RHODS Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster, DSCInitialization]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CRD]
    Dashboard -->|watches CRDs| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService, ServingRuntime]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| ModelRegistry[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CRD]
    Dashboard -.->|integrates API| DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Pipeline API]
    Dashboard -->|watches CRDs| Feast[Feast Operator<br/>FeatureStore CRD]
    Dashboard -->|watches CRDs| Ray[Ray Operator<br/>Distributed workloads]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| NIM[NVIDIA NIM<br/>Account CRD]
    Dashboard -->|queries metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>9091/HTTPS]

    %% Micro-frontend Dependencies (Modular Architecture)
    Dashboard -.->|module federation| MRUIFed[Model Registry UI<br/>micro-frontend]
    Dashboard -.->|module federation| GenAIFed[GenAI UI<br/>micro-frontend]
    Dashboard -.->|module federation| MaaSFed[MaaS UI<br/>micro-frontend]

    %% External Service Dependencies
    Dashboard -.->|model storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>AWS S3, MinIO]
    Dashboard -.->|image pulls| ImageReg[Image Registries<br/>Quay, RHOCP Registry]

    %% CRD Management
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| OdhApp[OdhApplication CRD<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    Dashboard -->|creates/manages| OdhConfig[OdhDashboardConfig CRD<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhDoc[OdhDocument CRD<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
    Dashboard -->|reads| OdhQuick[OdhQuickStart CRD<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]

